longBusinessSummary: Serviceware SE provides a portfolio of software solutions for the digitalization and automation of service processes in Germany, Austria, Switzerland, and internationally. The company offers enterprise service management platform, which includes anafee, a software tool for the financial management; helpline, a service management solution; Careware, a mobile and field service solution; Sabio, a knowledge management solution; and cubus, an integrated corporate planning software. It also provides IT infrastructure, software licensing, maintenance, Software as a Service, and managed services, as well as other support services. The company was founded in 1998 and is headquartered in Bad Camberg, Germany.
